# Deployment

## Environment Variables
```bash
# Development
EASYPOST_API_KEY=sk_test_...
ENVIRONMENT=development
DEBUG=true

# Production
EASYPOST_API_KEY=sk_live_...
ENVIRONMENT=production
DEBUG=false
CORS_ORIGINS=https://domain.com
```

## Pre-deployment Checklist
**Backend:**
- [ ] Tests passing
- [ ] No hardcoded credentials
- [ ] Error handling implemented
- [ ] CORS configured
- [ ] Health check working

**Frontend:**
- [ ] Tests passing
- [ ] Build succeeds
- [ ] No console errors
- [ ] Env vars configured
- [ ] HTTPS enforced

## Steps
1. Test locally
2. Create production build
3. Set production env vars
4. Deploy
5. Verify health endpoints
6. Monitor logs
